{"tid":1294210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集資打官司，告鳩班黑警！！（問）","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:32:09.000Z","uid":276064,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b0415d39d3045c049dda5389c6f965240463959c","tid":1294210,"uid":276064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"黑警亂９咁打人，又唔洗有代價，相信已經令各位好絕望！<br />\n<br />\n黑警放走打人藍絲、濫權亂打人、唔帶委任證、下令亂開槍、向人群／和平示威者掉催淚彈，種種黑警犯法行為而又無人可以制止佢地既情況下，有冇可能好似<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">入暗角七黑警罪</span></span>咁以法律途徑請大狀入稟法院控告佢地最大粒野，盧偉聰／白衫阿頭（eg: 陶輝) （<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集資打官司告</span></span>）。短期黎講可能阻止唔到，但長期黎講有阻嚇性。樂觀既話，一旦真係成功入罪，形勢就會逆轉。而且，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地有好多大律師公會既大狀企起我地哩邊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n小第唔識法律程序，唔知海外法庭裁決有冇用，唔知咁做可唔可行，希望讀ＬＡＷ既巴打可以出黎講幾句。<br />\n以下係幾個入稟告過警狗既幾個案例<br />\n採訪旺角騷亂疑遭警襲擊 記者入稟索償（ＮＯＷＴＶ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=336456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336456&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=1896d186\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336456&h=60c4f628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=336456</a><br />\n<br />\n監警會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/home/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhome%2Findex.html&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=f7a7d747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/home/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n東網（投訴成功率20190605）有幾高就自己睇啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/bkn-20190605092709123-0605_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190605%2Fbkn-20190605